   <Table name="Detection">
      <Title>
      Contains individual plate detections for every plate in the SSA.
      </Title>
      <Description>
                                                                                            
      Each scanned plate in the SSA results in a pixel map. This map
      was processed using standard software (known as Image Analysis Mode,
      or IAM, software) to produce a list of parameterised detections on each
      plate. This table contains all the attributes for each detected object.
      The attribute set consists of the standard 32 IAM parameters plus
      calibrated photometry and spatial index quantities.
      </Description>
